# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo and on checkout.
# Without this, Windows checkouts (core.autocrlf=true) produce CRLF working
# copies that fail Prettier's default `endOfLine: lf` check, while CI on Linux
# sees LF and passes — a confusing platform-only lint failure.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Keep binary assets untouched.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
